    {
      "id": "PopularPost225709",
      "post_content": "This + [Brood Sliver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brood Sliver) + [Heart Sliver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heart Sliver)/[Reflex Sliver](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reflex Sliver) + seed damage/spare sliver = all players dead.\n  \n   \nI'm planning to run an EDH sliver deck with those 3 and [Sliver Overlord](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sliver Overlord) as comander. Hopefully this will lead to some easy victories (but not too easy or I might never get to play EDH again).",
      "posted_by": "Bob_of_Mage",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost225709\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This + <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brood Sliver\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brood Sliver\">Brood Sliver</a> + <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Heart Sliver\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Heart Sliver\">Heart Sliver</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reflex Sliver\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reflex Sliver\">Reflex Sliver</a> + seed damage/spare sliver = all players dead. \r<br/> <br/>I'm planning to run an EDH sliver deck with those 3 and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sliver Overlord\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sliver Overlord\">Sliver Overlord</a> as comander. Hopefully this will lead to some easy victories (but not too easy or I might never get to play EDH again).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '225709'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy78561\">Bob_of_Mage</span>\r\n                                (2/2/2012 4:48:51 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRati