      "id": "PopularPost285104",
      "post_content": "I remember using this card in a UW sliver deck when it came out to show some of my friends who I just got into magic the evil of using slivers. After toying with everyone for a couple of turns (5 person multiplayer, like archenemy, everyone against me.), I proceeded to show them why using slivers = no more friends, by dropping an essence sliver and ended the game.   \n  \nAfter my first brush with slivers when I started playing around the masque block, I have been an advocate of the \"friends don't don't have friends who use slivers\" idea.",
